                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      <b>Avoid Overloading:</b>
                      <ul>
                        <li>
                          Why: Overloading the dryer can prevent clothes from
                          tumbling freely, leading to uneven drying.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          How: Stick to recommended load sizes and consider
                          splitting large loads into smaller ones.
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </li>

